{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "80b00b5d-bd8d-4403-a30d-7dc8d86eaf14", "type": 201, "content": {"answer_steps": [], "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/80b00b5d-bd8d-4403-a30d-7dc8d86eaf14@1.pkg/1772597544746/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597545380", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/80b00b5d-bd8d-4403-a30d-7dc8d86eaf14@1.pkg/1772597544746/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597545380"}, "identifier": "80b00b5d-bd8d-4403-a30d-7dc8d86eaf14", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>本题考查正确行使权利及法律责任的判定的相关知识。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>A:国家维护的是公民的合法权利，而非&ldquo;所有权利&rdquo;（非法权利不受保护），故A说法错误。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>B:公民行使权利时不得侵犯他人合法权利，&ldquo;开盒挂人&rdquo;非法公开他人隐私信息，侵犯隐私权、名誉权等，国家打击是为了维护权利与义务的统一，故B符合题意。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>C:违法行为需根据情节承担不同责任（如民事、行政或刑事），并非&ldquo;都要承担刑事责任&rdquo;，故C说法错误。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>D:&ldquo;开盒挂人&rdquo;直接违反法律，与权利义务相关，并非&ldquo;不道德行为&rdquo;，故D说法错误;故本题选B。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（原创）近日，新型网暴&ldquo;开盒挂人&rdquo;引发关注和热议。&ldquo;开盒挂人&rdquo; 是非法挖掘并公开他人隐私的新型网暴行为，国家加大打击力度，是因为（ &nbsp; &nbsp; ）​</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（原创）近日，新型网暴“开盒挂人”引发关注和热议。“开盒挂人” 是非法挖掘并公开他人隐私的新型网暴行为，国家加大打击力度，是因为（     ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/80b00b5d-bd8d-4403-a30d-7dc8d86eaf14@1.pkg/item.json?v=1755141462748", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>公民权利很广泛，国家维护公民所有权利​</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>行使权利有边界，开盒挂人侵犯他人权利​</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>该类行为违反法律，都要负刑事责任​</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>该行为仅属不道德行为，要加以制止</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（原创）近日，新型网暴&ldquo;开盒挂人&rdquo;引发关注和热议。&ldquo;开盒挂人&rdquo; 是非法挖掘并公开他人隐私的新型网暴行为，国家加大打击力度，是因为（ &nbsp; &nbsp; ）​</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "tags": ["$M002000000", "44bee8bc-54e6